				<div class="hvres-header">			<div class="hvres-definition no-word">			<p class="hvres-spell"><a href="/hv/tưởng">tưởng</a><span class="hvres-operations"> <i class="fas fa-link icon icon-hoverable" data-tippy-content="Copy liên kết" onclick="CopyURLToClipboard(location.origin+'/whv/獎#plc8f62a3c41')"></i></span>			</p>			<p class="hvres-info gray small">phồn thể</p>			</div>
